WEBVTT



00:00:13.439 --> 00:00:15.119
Why did you admit it?

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:16.879
I'm an orphan.

00:00:17.239 --> 00:00:19.159
I grew up under your wing.

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:20.959
Having you as my big brother in this life...

00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:22.319
It's worth it.

00:00:44.759 --> 00:00:45.439
Lin Shen.

00:00:45.799 --> 00:00:46.639
The case is solved.

00:01:17.080 --> 00:01:17.919
I'm sorry.

00:01:18.199 --> 00:01:19.639
The number you dialed...

00:01:19.639 --> 00:01:21.000
is not answering at the moment.

00:01:22.279 --> 00:01:23.120
The case is solved.

00:01:23.559 --> 00:01:24.360
Where are you?

00:01:27.839 --> 00:01:28.720
I'm sorry.

00:01:28.919 --> 00:01:30.360
The number you dialed...

00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:31.720
is not answering at the moment.

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.239
Please try again later.

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:08.759
Mom.

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:09.559
Lu Yi.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:11.199
You're finally back.

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:18.559
Did my dad wake up?

00:02:18.559 --> 00:02:20.000
Your dad's been the same this whole time.

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:21.759
Then did Lin Shen come by our place?

00:02:22.039 --> 00:02:22.800
Xiao Shen...

00:02:23.119 --> 00:02:24.000
She did come.

00:02:24.039 --> 00:02:24.800
She checked on your dad.

00:02:25.039 --> 00:02:26.199
Then she rushed off.

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:33.759
What's with that kid...

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:34.839
Mom, I gotta go.

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:36.520
Why are you leaving so soon?

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.240
When will you be back?

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:01.279
Boss.

00:03:01.679 --> 00:03:02.800
Has Lin Shen been here lately?

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:04.199
Lin Shen?

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:06.000
She hasn't been by in a long time.

00:03:38.639 --> 00:03:39.240
Lin Shen!

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:52.119
Lin Shen!

00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:53.919
Lin Shen!

00:03:56.119 --> 00:03:56.919
Lin Shen!

00:04:09.639 --> 00:04:10.919
What's wrong? We're on the same side.

00:04:10.919 --> 00:04:11.440
What "same side"?

00:04:11.440 --> 00:04:12.360
Who says I'm on your side?

00:04:12.559 --> 00:04:13.759
This one's with me.

00:04:13.759 --> 00:04:14.839
No need to hide it.

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:16.440
You've crossed the line.

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:18.480
From now on, I'm over here.

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:19.200
You're over there.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.480
If it were you...

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:24.399
you'd never abandon a friend, right?

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:26.000
Of course.

00:04:26.559 --> 00:04:28.640
As your friend, I'm protecting you.

00:04:28.640 --> 00:04:30.160
What kind of friend is that, Lin Shen?

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:30.880
Do I have any friends?

00:04:30.880 --> 00:04:32.160
Do you think I have friends?

00:04:32.239 --> 00:04:33.320
Aren't I?

00:04:37.799 --> 00:04:39.160
Avoid cold drinks for a couple of days.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:40.880
I don't want to write in the mission report...

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:42.320
that you got hurt because of period cramps.

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:43.679
If you're worried about me,

00:04:43.679 --> 00:04:44.720
then just say you're worried about me.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:55.959
Wake up, Lu Yi.

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:58.079
You're hurt.

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:04.920
Lu Yi.

00:05:05.279 --> 00:05:05.920
Don't let go.

00:05:06.440 --> 00:05:07.160
Hold tight.

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.119
Thank you, Lin Shen.

00:05:15.119 --> 00:05:16.119
You saved me once.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:18.480
Twice.

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:21.079
Why are you so petty?

00:05:36.119 --> 00:05:36.839
Lin Shen.

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:01.720
I read that newspaper.

00:06:02.679 --> 00:06:03.640
A man who hits women...

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:06.920
deserves to die.

00:06:19.119 --> 00:06:20.839
And he still asks you for money?

00:06:21.200 --> 00:06:22.239
What gives him the right?

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:23.880
Brother.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:24.839
I'm telling you,

00:06:25.399 --> 00:06:27.079
if you don't deal with this woman,

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.440
then for the rest of your life...

00:06:28.760 --> 00:06:29.440
you're finished.

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:30.839
Trust your big brother.

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:49.720
People who don't respect life

00:06:51.679 --> 00:06:52.880
should all die.

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:56.640
They should return to where life

00:06:57.640 --> 00:06:58.920
first began.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:13.000
I want to kill him.

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:15.640
Is there anything

00:07:16.119 --> 00:07:17.200
I can do to help you?

00:07:33.880 --> 00:07:35.799
He used the deli as an observation post.

00:07:35.799 --> 00:07:37.920
He singled out those living on the margins,

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:40.239
filled with resentment and bitterness.

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:41.720
Liu Ping's cowardice.

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:42.959
Ling Han's low self-esteem.

00:07:43.079 --> 00:07:44.239
Cao Feng's greed.

00:07:44.440 --> 00:07:45.679
Zeng Lili's despair.

00:07:46.239 --> 00:07:47.399
He didn't do it directly.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.720
He used words as a knife,

00:07:48.760 --> 00:07:49.959
precisely slicing open

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.320
the wounds in their hearts.

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:52.079
Then,

00:07:52.239 --> 00:07:53.720
he sprinkled on the salt of hatred.

00:08:11.559 --> 00:08:12.160
Lin Shen.

00:08:14.079 --> 00:08:14.959
Where on earth are you?

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:33.400
Captain Duan.

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:39.359
You're awake.

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:43.320
How do you feel?

00:08:43.840 --> 00:08:44.520
The doctor said

00:08:44.520 --> 00:08:45.679
you're just overworked.

00:08:45.679 --> 00:08:46.400
Overworked,

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:47.559
and this sudden stress hit you hard,

00:08:47.719 --> 00:08:48.359
that's why this happened.

00:08:48.359 --> 00:08:49.000
It's nothing serious.

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:49.719
Where's Lin Shen?

00:08:50.799 --> 00:08:51.799
Any news?

00:08:53.280 --> 00:08:53.880
Not yet.

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:55.719
We've expanded the search area.

00:08:59.599 --> 00:09:00.239
Captain Duan.

00:09:01.039 --> 00:09:01.919
I want to be discharged.

00:09:02.719 --> 00:09:03.840
No, the doctor already said it.

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:04.599
I can't just lie here.

00:09:04.599 --> 00:09:05.320
You just got your fever down.

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:06.440
You can't leave.

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:07.520
I have to get back to the station.

00:09:07.520 --> 00:09:08.320
I...

00:09:08.479 --> 00:09:09.719
I have to go to work.

00:09:13.359 --> 00:09:13.880
Captain Duan.

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:14.880
Captain Duan!

00:09:18.400 --> 00:09:19.880
You're really stubborn.

00:09:20.559 --> 00:09:21.679
You really make people worry.

00:09:39.359 --> 00:09:40.039
Boss Hu

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:41.479
Hu Jianjun

00:09:42.400 --> 00:09:44.599
is the hidden nexus of all the cases

00:09:45.080 --> 00:09:46.799
Everyone's been to his braised food shop

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:48.039
more or less

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.440
and had some connection

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:50.440
Also

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:52.919
on the note Lin Shen left

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.359
my dad left her

00:09:54.359 --> 00:09:55.479
a piece of Morse code

00:09:55.719 --> 00:09:56.760
It translates to

00:09:57.520 --> 00:09:58.320
left hand

00:09:58.919 --> 00:09:59.960
So I'm thinking

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:02.239
maybe my dad realized back then that

00:10:02.239 --> 00:10:04.239
the attacker was left-handed

00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:05.559
And Hu Jianjun

00:10:06.719 --> 00:10:07.760
is a lefty

00:10:08.919 --> 00:10:09.919
You mean

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:11.119
the Thirteenth Middle School case

00:10:11.119 --> 00:10:12.400
and the recent murders

00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:14.119
even Lin Shen's disappearance

00:10:14.599 --> 00:10:16.080
are all connected to this guy

00:10:17.599 --> 00:10:19.599
Lin Shen has been suspecting him lately

00:10:20.239 --> 00:10:22.080
Maybe he already sensed it

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:24.239
So Lin Shen's disappearance

00:10:24.559 --> 00:10:25.760
is very likely tied to him

00:10:29.919 --> 00:10:31.080
This guy is really sly.

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:32.679
Sister Shen went to his shop

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:34.159
but she didn't find anything

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:35.479
Haozi

00:10:36.119 --> 00:10:37.359
Try to recover

00:10:37.359 --> 00:10:38.559
from all the victims' phones

00:10:38.559 --> 00:10:39.919
the chat app data

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:40.919
I'll go right now

00:10:45.679 --> 00:10:47.840
The storm hanging over this city

00:10:48.679 --> 00:10:49.599
needs to end

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:58.039
Killing one

00:10:58.559 --> 00:10:59.320
is still killing

00:11:00.280 --> 00:11:01.359
Killing two

00:11:01.919 --> 00:11:02.840
is still killing

00:11:09.719 --> 00:11:11.799
Then when I begged you back then

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:14.919
why didn't you spare me

00:11:19.559 --> 00:11:22.039
Hu Jianjun was bullied as a kid

00:11:22.400 --> 00:11:24.359
and ran into them again as an adult

00:11:24.799 --> 00:11:26.239
Driven by revenge

00:11:26.640 --> 00:11:28.400
he brutally killed them

00:11:29.559 --> 00:11:30.640
One killing

00:11:30.640 --> 00:11:32.359
seemed to unleash his inner demon,

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:34.000
and there was no turning back.

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:37.599
Brother

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:39.559
Stab her

00:11:58.200 --> 00:11:59.520
Bright red blood

00:11:59.919 --> 00:12:01.919
was like the finest velvet

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:04.239
the most beautiful color I'd ever seen

00:12:05.840 --> 00:12:06.840
From then on

00:12:07.559 --> 00:12:09.119
he realized doing it himself

00:12:09.280 --> 00:12:10.520
was nothing special

00:12:11.679 --> 00:12:12.679
So he started trying every trick

00:12:12.679 --> 00:12:14.280
to incite others to commit crimes

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:18.280
Turning those with knots in their hearts

00:12:18.719 --> 00:12:20.559
into knives in his hand

00:12:24.039 --> 00:12:24.719
Hu Jianjun

00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:26.919
Lu Yi

00:12:27.799 --> 00:12:28.640
Why are you here?

00:12:35.479 --> 00:12:36.359
Why am I here?

00:12:39.400 --> 00:12:40.320
I looked at your whiteboard

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:41.320
All the clues point

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.000
right here

00:12:42.719 --> 00:12:43.520
I found this place

00:12:43.520 --> 00:12:44.200
so I found you

00:12:44.200 --> 00:12:45.159
If I hadn't found this place,

00:12:45.159 --> 00:12:45.880
were you planning to

00:12:45.880 --> 00:12:46.799
never show up again?

00:12:47.960 --> 00:12:49.039
Where have you been these days?

00:12:49.479 --> 00:12:50.919
Why were you here all alone?

00:12:50.919 --> 00:12:52.479
Do you know how worried I've been?

00:12:52.559 --> 00:12:53.359
Do you know

00:12:53.359 --> 00:12:54.679
at the Thirteenth Middle School gate

00:12:54.679 --> 00:12:56.239
I picked up the little hair tie I gave you

00:12:56.239 --> 00:12:57.679
I thought something happened to you

00:13:09.280 --> 00:13:10.080
I'm fine

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.239
Don't worry

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.679
I've been carrying that hair tie

00:13:16.400 --> 00:13:17.320
It's just that today

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:18.400
I don't know when I dropped it

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:21.359
My time off was fake.

00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:25.440
Lu Yi

00:13:25.880 --> 00:13:27.119
I can tell you now

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.520
Higher-ups had me investigating a case

00:13:29.840 --> 00:13:31.200
This case goes very deep.

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:32.919
But now I

00:13:33.320 --> 00:13:34.520
have found key evidence

00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:39.080
Take a look at this first

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:40.799
What is this?

00:13:42.599 --> 00:13:43.640
Hu Jianjun's trophies

00:13:44.760 --> 00:13:46.520
and the answer to all our questions

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:52.719
These clay figurines

00:13:53.359 --> 00:13:54.000
Look familiar?

00:14:00.799 --> 00:14:01.919
The one missing a finger

00:14:03.799 --> 00:14:04.679
is Liu Ping

00:14:11.359 --> 00:14:12.520
The one with a slightly swollen belly

00:14:13.520 --> 00:14:14.239
is Zhou Shuyu

00:14:19.640 --> 00:14:20.400
This one

00:14:21.080 --> 00:14:22.000
is Zeng Lili

00:14:37.239 --> 00:14:38.039
This is

00:14:42.679 --> 00:14:44.200
my dad's wedding ring

00:14:49.359 --> 00:14:50.320
This Hu Jianjun

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:53.320
collected all the victims' belongings

00:14:54.960 --> 00:14:56.400
and put them in plain sight

00:14:57.119 --> 00:14:58.640
admiring them again and again every day

00:15:02.880 --> 00:15:03.440
Lu Yi

00:15:05.479 --> 00:15:07.039
The person you've always brooded over,

00:15:07.599 --> 00:15:08.880
the one in that photo,

00:15:09.559 --> 00:15:10.320
is my uncle.

00:15:13.919 --> 00:15:14.640
A few years ago

00:15:15.039 --> 00:15:16.000
he died in a car accident

00:15:17.440 --> 00:15:18.640
but I don't think it was an accident

00:15:20.559 --> 00:15:21.640
Your uncle

00:15:22.799 --> 00:15:24.440
how is he tied to this case?

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:28.840
Behind this Hu Jianjun

00:15:29.479 --> 00:15:31.559
there's a bigger criminal gang

00:15:32.359 --> 00:15:33.359
What happened to your dad

00:15:33.919 --> 00:15:34.799
my uncle's death

00:15:35.359 --> 00:15:36.599
are inextricably linked to him.

00:15:45.960 --> 00:15:47.359
Right under my nose

00:15:49.599 --> 00:15:50.880
the killer who ruined my dad

00:15:51.919 --> 00:15:52.760
and the evidence

00:15:54.039 --> 00:15:55.359
were right under my nose

00:15:56.679 --> 00:15:58.119
and I didn't notice a thing

00:16:02.440 --> 00:16:03.719
But the truth is close now

00:16:05.719 --> 00:16:06.760
We'll get justice for your dad

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:09.000
and all the other victims.

00:16:09.799 --> 00:16:10.599
We'll make them pay.